title: McLevy Series 1 - 10
description:
42 x 45 mins

McLevy is a Victorian detective series, featuring Inspector James McLevy, his sidekick PC Mulholland, his boss the whining social climber Lieutenant Roache (played by the author David Ashton) and the local bawdy house keeper, the beautiful Jean Brash, the Queen of Crime, with whom McLevy has an increasingly flirtatious relationship.

The storyline and the relationship between the characters develops across each series, though each episode remains a well crafted, self-contained story.
